						<p>On the north wall of the first <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> in the Vēdāraṇyēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Rājarāja III. Year 24: 1239-40 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This records the sale and dedication of two slaves Kaḻani and Kuḍiyāḷ by Ariyan Pichchaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Gaṅgaināḍāḻvāṉ to god Tirumaṟaikkāḍ-uḍaiyār. </p>						

